<li>Information sabotage</li>
<li>Product tampering</li>
<li>Workplace bombing</li>
<li>Natural disaster that destroys organizational office</li>
<li>Computer tampering</li>
<li>Sexual harassment</li>
<li>Natural disaster that disrupts product/service</li>
<li>Confidential data loss</li>
<li>Kidnapping, (Key person; Tiger)</li>
<li>Product/service boycott</li>
<li>Work-related homicide</li>
<li>Malicious rumor</li>
