<li><a href="http://www.crisisexperts.com" class="external text" title="http://www.crisisexperts.com" rel="nofollow">Institute for Crisis Management</a>,an international company specializing in crisis communication management planning, training and consulting.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.sourcewatch.org/index.php?title=Crisis_management" class="external text" title="http://www.sourcewatch.org/index.php?title=Crisis_management" rel="nofollow">Source Watch</a>. Center for Media and Democracy. Crisis Management Entry.</li>
